SOUTH AFRICA.
RADIO SERVICES.
1. ON 31 AUG SOUTH AFRICA'S INTERNATIONAL AND
   DOMESTIC TELEX SERVICES WILL BE DISCONTINUED.
2. PRE-ARRIVAL / PRE-ENTRY REPORTS MUST
   BE SENT TO CAPE TOWN RADIO VIA
   E-MAIL: MARITIMERADIO@IXMAIL.CO.ZA.
   NO ATTACHMENTS ALLOWED. ENTIRE CONTENTS
   OF REPORT MUST BE PLACED INSIDE BODY
   OF MSG AS PLAIN TEXT.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 31 AUG 13.
